# OttoLog project overview

## Stack

Expo ~57 / React Native / TypeScript / Supabase. Before Expo APIs: https://docs.expo.dev/versions/v57.0.0/

## Layout

- App code: `src/` (+ `App.tsx`)
- SQL migrations: `sql/greenfield/` (canonical) — apply in order per `docs/Setup.md`; `sql/deprecated/` is historical only
- Canonical docs: `docs/*.md`
- **Ignore** `docs/deprecated/` (historical only; not the contract)

